com.poesys.accounting.dataloader.oldaccounting

Class Reimbursement

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.poesys.accounting.dataloader.oldaccounting.AbstractReaderDto
      • com.poesys.accounting.dataloader.oldaccounting.Reimbursement

  • public class Reimbursement
extends AbstractReaderDto
    A data transfer object that holds raw data for a reimbursement item; used to construct the old accounting reimbursement item object and to link up to receivables; the amounts are positive, representing credits to the receivables account. Fields: reimbursement transaction id, receivable year, receivable transaction id, receivable account #, reimbursed amount, allocated amount
    Author:
    Robert J. Muller
